name: larry-dev-router
description: Route skill selection for Larry's common development work. Use when starting a task in the user's repos and Codex needs to choose among installed skills based on task intent, nearby project files, and the current stack. Most useful for React, Next.js, Vite, Vue, Python, and .NET projects before implementation or review begins.
